The below installations should be done to allow the python script to crawl the web.
Try to integrate these steps into an image for Kubernetes.

1. Installing pip
2. Python 3.4.2
3. Installing the "Pandas" package
4. Installing the Bs4 (beautifulsoup) package
5. Installing the webdriver (chrome) in PATH
6. installing selenium

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get intall python3
sudo apt install python-pip
pip install selenium
apt-get install python3-bs4
pip install beautifulsoup4
pip install pandas
wget https://dl.google.com/linux/direct/google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb
sudo dpkg -i google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb
sudo apt-get install chromium-chromedriver
